FIRST INSTRUCTIONS
------------------

This package contains both ready-to-run executables and source code.

Documentation is in the doc/ directory.  Everything you need to know about
installing and using the current package is in manual.txt.  The rel* files
contain details about changes between various versions and upgrading.txt
contains instructions for upgraders if necessary.


----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Contact details 
--------------- 

There is no fee for drealmBBS software. There is no warranty for it either
(see the file COPYING).  However, if you wish, you may send a donation as we
spend our own personal cash and time on running and maintaining the
development BBS!!!


Email:		inge@drealm.org.uk
		inge@drealm.clara.co.uk

Usenet: 	alt.bbs.drealmbbs (not used much now except for announcements)


